{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":724,"text":"Women represent"},{"time":2523,"text":"50 percent of middle management"},{"time":5574,"text":"and professional positions,"},{"time":8363,"text":"but the percentages of women\nat the top of organizations"},{"time":11491,"text":"represent not even a third of that number."},{"time":14315,"text":"So some people hear that statistic and they ask,"},{"time":17820,"text":"why do we have so few women leaders?"},{"time":21323,"text":"But I look at that statistic"},{"time":23246,"text":"and, if you, like me, believe"},{"time":26020,"text":"that leadership manifests at every level,"},{"time":29800,"text":"you would see that there's a tremendous,"},{"time":32786,"text":"awesome resource of leaders"},{"time":35767,"text":"who are leading in middle management,"},{"time":38523,"text":"which raises a different question:"},{"time":41639,"text":"Why are there so many women"},{"time":43889,"text":"mired in the middle"},{"time":45880,"text":"and what has to happen"},{"time":47702,"text":"to take them to the top?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":50245,"text":"So some of you might be some of those women"},{"time":52764,"text":"who are in middle management"},{"time":54587,"text":"and seeking to move up in your organization."},{"time":58513,"text":"Well, Tonya is a great example\nof one of these women."},{"time":62135,"text":"I met her two years ago."},{"time":63834,"text":"She was a vice president in a Fortune 50 company,"},{"time":67170,"text":"and she said to me with a sense of deep frustration,"},{"time":71393,"text":"\"I've worked really hard to improve my confidence"},{"time":74791,"text":"and my assertiveness and develop a great brand,"},{"time":78154,"text":"I get terrific performance evals from my boss,"},{"time":81979,"text":"my 360s in the organization let me know"},{"time":85218,"text":"that my teams love working for me,"},{"time":88515,"text":"I've taken every management course that I can here,"},{"time":92351,"text":"I am working with a terrific mentor,"},{"time":94916,"text":"and yet I've been passed over"},{"time":97334,"text":"twice for advancement opportunities,"},{"time":100507,"text":"even when my manager knows"},{"time":102790,"text":"that I'm committed to moving up"},{"time":104601,"text":"and even interested in an international assignment."},{"time":109236,"text":"I don't understand why"},{"time":111148,"text":"I'm being passed over.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":113117,"text":"So what Tonya doesn't realize"},{"time":115345,"text":"is that there's a missing 33 percent"},{"time":118369,"text":"of the career success equation for women,"},{"time":121990,"text":"and it's understanding what this missing 33 percent is"},{"time":125815,"text":"that's required to close the gender gap at the top."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130529,"text":"In order to move up in organizations,"},{"time":133543,"text":"you have to be known for your leadership skills,"},{"time":136162,"text":"and this would apply to any of you,"},{"time":137741,"text":"women or men."},{"time":140290,"text":"It means that you have to be recognized"},{"time":143294,"text":"for using the greatness in you"},{"time":145971,"text":"to achieve and sustain extraordinary outcomes"},{"time":149222,"text":"by engaging the greatness in others."},{"time":152901,"text":"Put in other language,"},{"time":154291,"text":"it means you have to use your skills"},{"time":156309,"text":"and talents and abilities"},{"time":158705,"text":"to help the organization achieve"},{"time":161113,"text":"its strategic financial goals"},{"time":164262,"text":"and do that by working effectively with others"},{"time":167907,"text":"inside of the organization and outside."},{"time":171901,"text":"And although all three of these elements"},{"time":174196,"text":"of leadership are important,"},{"time":176232,"text":"when it comes to moving up in organizations,"},{"time":178931,"text":"they aren't equally important."},{"time":180788,"text":"So pay attention to the green box"},{"time":183533,"text":"as I move forward."}]},{"cues":[{"time":187548,"text":"In seeking and identifying"},{"time":190340,"text":"employees with high potential,"},{"time":192357,"text":"the potential to go to the top of organizations,"},{"time":197006,"text":"the skills and competencies"},{"time":200400,"text":"that relate to that green box"},{"time":202380,"text":"are rated twice as heavily"},{"time":204753,"text":"as those in the other two elements of leadership."},{"time":208567,"text":"These skills and competencies"},{"time":210637,"text":"can be summarized as business,"},{"time":213337,"text":"strategic, and financial acumen."},{"time":216509,"text":"In other words, this skill set has to do"},{"time":219170,"text":"with understanding where the organization is going,"},{"time":223483,"text":"what its strategy is,"},{"time":225621,"text":"what financial targets it has in place,"},{"time":228140,"text":"and understanding your role"},{"time":229570,"text":"in moving the organization forward."},{"time":232247,"text":"This is that missing 33 percent"},{"time":236445,"text":"of the career success equation for women,"},{"time":239425,"text":"not because it's missing in our capabilities"},{"time":241978,"text":"or abilities,"},{"time":243598,"text":"but because it's missing in the advice"},{"time":245724,"text":"that we're given."}]},{"cues":[{"time":247378,"text":"Here's what I mean by that."},{"time":249147,"text":"Five years ago, I was asked to moderate"},{"time":251338,"text":"a panel of executives,"},{"time":253171,"text":"and the topic for the evening was"},{"time":255160,"text":"\"What do you look for in \nhigh-potential employees?\""},{"time":258538,"text":"So think about the three elements of leadership"},{"time":261620,"text":"as I summarize for you what they told me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264410,"text":"They said, \"We look for people"},{"time":266907,"text":"who are smart and hard working and committed"},{"time":270563,"text":"and trustworthy and resilient.\""},{"time":274669,"text":"So which element of leadership does that relate to?"},{"time":278503,"text":"Personal greatness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":280519,"text":"They said, \"We look for employees"},{"time":283200,"text":"who are great with our customers,"},{"time":285529,"text":"who empower their teams,"},{"time":287723,"text":"who negotiate effectively,"},{"time":289781,"text":"who are able to manage conflict well,"},{"time":292324,"text":"and are overall great communicators.\""},{"time":295564,"text":"Which element of leadership does that equate to?"},{"time":298874,"text":"Engaging the greatness in others."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301683,"text":"And then they pretty much stopped."},{"time":303889,"text":"So I asked,"},{"time":305120,"text":"\"Well, what about people"},{"time":307170,"text":"who understand your business,"},{"time":309534,"text":"where it's going,"},{"time":310940,"text":"and their role in taking it there?"},{"time":313550,"text":"And what about people who are able"},{"time":314866,"text":"to scan the external environment,"},{"time":317375,"text":"identify risks and opportunities,"},{"time":320176,"text":"make strategy or make strategic recommendations?"},{"time":324595,"text":"And what about people who are able"},{"time":326980,"text":"to look at the financials of your business,"},{"time":329558,"text":"understand the story that the financials tell,"},{"time":333202,"text":"and either take appropriate action"},{"time":335470,"text":"or make appropriate recommendations?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":338209,"text":"And to a man, they said,"},{"time":340155,"text":"\"That's a given.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":342347,"text":"So I turned to the audience"},{"time":343945,"text":"of 150 women and I asked,"},{"time":346976,"text":"\"How many of you have ever been told"},{"time":349878,"text":"that the door-opener for career advancement"},{"time":352837,"text":"is your business, strategic and financial acumen,"},{"time":356616,"text":"and that all the other important stuff"},{"time":359040,"text":"is what differentiates you in the talent pool?\""},{"time":362837,"text":"Three women raised their hand,"},{"time":365965,"text":"and I've asked this question of women"},{"time":368100,"text":"all around the globe in the five years since,"},{"time":370644,"text":"and the percentage is never much different."}]},{"cues":[{"time":375358,"text":"So this is obvious, right?"},{"time":377495,"text":"But how can it be?"},{"time":379407,"text":"Well, there are primarily three reasons"},{"time":381443,"text":"that there's this missing 33 percent"},{"time":383466,"text":"in the career success advice given to women?"},{"time":387101,"text":"When organizations direct women"},{"time":389630,"text":"toward resources"},{"time":391497,"text":"that focus on the conventional advice"},{"time":393830,"text":"that we've been hearing for over 40 years,"},{"time":395798,"text":"there's a notable absence of advice that relates"},{"time":399804,"text":"to business, strategic and financial acumen."},{"time":402952,"text":"Much of the advice is emphasizing"},{"time":405787,"text":"personal actions that we need to take,"},{"time":407621,"text":"like become more assertive, become more confident,"},{"time":410321,"text":"develop your personal brand,"},{"time":412030,"text":"things that Tonya's been working on,"},{"time":414854,"text":"and advice about working with other people,"},{"time":417381,"text":"things like learn to self-promote,"},{"time":420200,"text":"get a mentor, enhance your network,"},{"time":422365,"text":"and virtually nothing said"},{"time":424997,"text":"about the importance of business, strategic"},{"time":427070,"text":"and financial acumen."},{"time":429294,"text":"This doesn't mean that this advice is unimportant."},{"time":433397,"text":"What it means is that this is advice"},{"time":436111,"text":"that's absolutely essential for breaking through"},{"time":439115,"text":"from career start to middle management,"},{"time":443513,"text":"but it's not the advice"},{"time":445257,"text":"that gets women to break through"},{"time":447507,"text":"from the middle, where we're 50 percent,"},{"time":449824,"text":"to senior and executive positions."},{"time":452377,"text":"And this is why conventional advice to women"},{"time":455437,"text":"in 40 years hasn't closed the gender gap at the top"},{"time":459532,"text":"and won't close it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":462434,"text":"Now, the second reason"},{"time":464279,"text":"relates to Tonya's comments"},{"time":465967,"text":"about having had excellent performance evals,"},{"time":470418,"text":"great feedback from her teams,"},{"time":473069,"text":"and having taken every management training program"},{"time":475686,"text":"she can lay her hands on."},{"time":477756,"text":"So you would think that she's getting"},{"time":480708,"text":"messages from her organization"},{"time":483064,"text":"through the talent development systems"},{"time":485271,"text":"and performance management systems"},{"time":487745,"text":"that let her know how important it is"},{"time":489680,"text":"to develop business, strategic and financial acumen,"},{"time":493141,"text":"but here again, that green square is quite small."},{"time":497746,"text":"On average,"},{"time":499523,"text":"talent and performance management systems"},{"time":501829,"text":"in the organizations that I've worked with"},{"time":504383,"text":"focus three to one"},{"time":506858,"text":"on the other two elements of leadership"},{"time":509186,"text":"compared to the importance of business,"},{"time":511672,"text":"strategic and financial acumen,"},{"time":514203,"text":"which is why typical talent and performance systems"},{"time":518748,"text":"haven't closed and won't close"},{"time":520711,"text":"the gender gap at the top."}]},{"cues":[{"time":523968,"text":"Now, Tonya also talked about working with a mentor,"},{"time":527840,"text":"and this is really important to talk about,"},{"time":530279,"text":"because if organizations,"},{"time":531900,"text":"talent and performance systems"},{"time":533754,"text":"aren't giving people in general"},{"time":535571,"text":"information about the importance of"},{"time":538187,"text":"business, strategic and financial acumen,"},{"time":540527,"text":"how are men getting to the top?"},{"time":542744,"text":"Well, there are primarily two ways."},{"time":545263,"text":"One is because of the positions"},{"time":547130,"text":"they're guided into,"},{"time":549222,"text":"and the other is because of informal mentoring"},{"time":552193,"text":"and sponsorship."}]},{"cues":[{"time":553947,"text":"So what's women's experience"},{"time":555702,"text":"as it relates to mentoring?"},{"time":557907,"text":"Well, this comment from an executive"},{"time":560809,"text":"that I worked with recently"},{"time":562586,"text":"illustrates that experience."},{"time":564611,"text":"He was very proud of the fact that last year,"},{"time":567266,"text":"he had two protégés: a man and a woman."},{"time":571250,"text":"And he said, \"I helped the woman build confidence,"},{"time":574927,"text":"I helped the man learn the business,"},{"time":577346,"text":"and I didn't realize that I was treating them"},{"time":579753,"text":"any differently.\""},{"time":581227,"text":"And he was sincere about that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":583645,"text":"So what this illustrates is that"},{"time":585840,"text":"as managers, whether we're women or men,"},{"time":588230,"text":"we have mindsets about women and men,"},{"time":590260,"text":"about careers in leadership,"},{"time":592127,"text":"and these unexamined mindsets"},{"time":595150,"text":"won't close the gender gap at the top."},{"time":598922,"text":"So how do we take this idea"},{"time":600670,"text":"of the missing 33 percent"},{"time":602713,"text":"and turn it into action?"},{"time":604884,"text":"Well, for women, the answer is obvious:"},{"time":608281,"text":"we have to begin to focus more"},{"time":610554,"text":"on developing and demonstrating"},{"time":612491,"text":"the skills we have"},{"time":614190,"text":"that show that we're people who understand"},{"time":616639,"text":"our businesses, where they're headed,"},{"time":618912,"text":"and our role in taking it there."},{"time":621330,"text":"That's what enables that breakthrough"},{"time":623726,"text":"from middle management"},{"time":625999,"text":"to leadership at the top."},{"time":628867,"text":"But you don't have to be a middle manager to do this."},{"time":631230,"text":"One young scientist that works in a biotech firm"},{"time":634931,"text":"used her insight about the missing 33 percent"},{"time":639300,"text":"to weave financial impact data"},{"time":642412,"text":"into a project update she did"},{"time":644402,"text":"and got tremendous positive feedback"},{"time":646742,"text":"from the managers in the room."}]},{"cues":[{"time":649364,"text":"So we don't want to put 100 percent"},{"time":651614,"text":"of the responsibility on women's shoulders,"},{"time":655123,"text":"nor would it be wise to do so, and here's why:"},{"time":659443,"text":"In order for companies to achieve"},{"time":661209,"text":"their strategic financial goals,"},{"time":663886,"text":"executives understand that they have to have"},{"time":665844,"text":"everyone pulling in the same direction."},{"time":668600,"text":"In other words, the term we use in business is,"},{"time":671142,"text":"we have to have strategic alignment."},{"time":673801,"text":"And executives know this very well,"},{"time":676952,"text":"and yet only 37 percent,"},{"time":679281,"text":"according to a recent Conference Board report,"},{"time":681901,"text":"believe that they have that"},{"time":683499,"text":"strategic alignment in place."},{"time":686222,"text":"So for 63 percent of organizations,"},{"time":689900,"text":"achieving their strategic financial goals"},{"time":692217,"text":"is questionable."},{"time":693973,"text":"And if you think about what I've just shared,"},{"time":697156,"text":"that you have situations where at least 50 percent"},{"time":700126,"text":"of your middle managers"},{"time":701847,"text":"haven't received clear messaging"},{"time":704446,"text":"that they have to become focused on the business,"},{"time":708230,"text":"where it's headed, and their role in taking it there,"},{"time":710768,"text":"it's not surprising that that percentage"},{"time":712860,"text":"of executives who are confident about alignment"},{"time":715240,"text":"is so low,"},{"time":716937,"text":"which is why there are other people"},{"time":719906,"text":"who have a role to play in this."},{"time":722292,"text":"It's important for directors on boards"},{"time":725757,"text":"to expect from their executives"},{"time":728749,"text":"proportional pools of women when they sit down"},{"time":731268,"text":"once a year for their succession discussions."},{"time":733856,"text":"Why? Because if they aren't seeing that,"},{"time":736961,"text":"it could be a red flag"},{"time":738749,"text":"that their organization isn't as aligned"},{"time":741641,"text":"as it could potentially be."},{"time":744149,"text":"It's important for CEOs"},{"time":745645,"text":"to also expect these proportional pools,"},{"time":748469,"text":"and if they hear comments like,"},{"time":749976,"text":"\"Well, she doesn't have\nenough business experience,\""},{"time":752519,"text":"ask the question,"},{"time":754050,"text":"\"What are we going to do about that?\""},{"time":756174,"text":"It's important for H.R. executives"},{"time":758323,"text":"to make sure that the missing 33 percent"},{"time":760955,"text":"is appropriately emphasized,"},{"time":763116,"text":"and it's important for women and men"},{"time":765219,"text":"who are in management positions"},{"time":767277,"text":"to examine the mindsets we hold"},{"time":769420,"text":"about women and men, about careers and success,"},{"time":771687,"text":"to make sure we are creating a level playing field"},{"time":774398,"text":"for everybody."}]},{"cues":[{"time":776322,"text":"So let me close with the latest chapter"},{"time":778245,"text":"in Tonya's story."},{"time":780080,"text":"Tonya emailed me two months ago,"},{"time":781924,"text":"and she said that she had been\ninterviewed for a new position,"},{"time":784838,"text":"and during the interview, they probed"},{"time":786649,"text":"about her business acumen"},{"time":788178,"text":"and her strategic insights into the industry,"},{"time":791407,"text":"and she said that she was so happy to report"},{"time":793871,"text":"that now she has a new position"},{"time":795829,"text":"reporting directly to the \nchief information officer"},{"time":798922,"text":"at her company."},{"time":801138,"text":"So for some of you, the missing 33 percent"},{"time":803714,"text":"is an idea for you to put into action,"},{"time":806695,"text":"and I hope that for all of you,"},{"time":808956,"text":"you will see it as an idea worth spreading"},{"time":812108,"text":"in order to help organizations be more effective,"},{"time":814581,"text":"to help women create careers that soar,"},{"time":817157,"text":"and to help close the gender gap at the top."}]},{"cues":[{"time":820761,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":822584,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}